export type GrammarDifficulty = 'easy' | 'medium' | 'hard';
export type GrammarCategory = 'basic' | 'particles' | 'verbs' | 'adjectives' | 'all';

  japanese: string;
  english: string;
  category: GrammarCategory;
  difficulty: GrammarDifficulty;
  pattern: string;
  hint?: string;

  // Basic Patterns (Easy)
